OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy to start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain or drizzle. Cloud will
OL,7,Fclear from the east through the
OL,8,Fmorning, with long afternoon sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Fresh winds, strengthening
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright evening, with plenty
OL,13,Fof late sunny spells. Mostly clear
OL,14,Fovernight, becoming rather cool in
OL,15,Frural parts. Fresh to strong winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,18,Fsunny spells, though tempered by the
OL,19,Ffresh to strong easterly wind. Cooler
OL,20,Fnear coasts where winds will be
OL,21,Fstrongest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
